bilingual.source: Space-based science has helped farming in its efforts to grow enough food.
bilingual.target: 基于太空的科学帮助农业努力种植足够的食物。

bilingual.source: We saw a lot of interesting things and we learned a lot from him about farming.
bilingual.target: 我们看到了很多有趣的东西，并从他那里学到了很多关于农业的知识。
农业社会依赖于农业生产。

bilingual.source: The agribusiness invested heavily in new farming technology.
bilingual.target: 这家农业综合企业在新农业技术上进行了大量投资。

bilingual.source: The sickle is a traditional farming tool.
bilingual.target: 镰刀是传统的农业工具。

bilingual.source: Agritourism can help educate people about sustainable farming practices.
bilingual.target: 农业旅游可以帮助人们了解可持续农业实践。

bilingual.source: Organic farming is better for the environment.
bilingual.target: 有机的农业对环境更好。
农业是一种劳动密集型的职业。

bilingual.source: Modern tools have made farming much easier.
bilingual.target: 现代工具使农业变得更加容易。

bilingual.source: Many families rely on farming for their livelihood.
bilingual.target: 许多家庭依靠农业为生。

list.abstract: farming，英语单词，主要用作为名词，动词，用作名词译为“ 农业，耕作”，用作动词译为“耕种；出租（farm的ing形式）”。

yingyinNormal.en: Because farming allowed us to come together in bigger and bigger groups, to build villages, towns, and eventually cities.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为农业让我们人类以更大的团体而群居，这样才能建造村落，小镇，直到都市。

yingyinNormal.en: Our ancestors must have felt that they were the masters of this new crop, in the same way that we still feel today about farming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的祖先一定会觉得他们是这种新植物的主人，和我们现在对于农业的认识是一样的。

yingyinNormal.en: And so we're farming the land here and the mill is that close.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在这里耕种，磨坊就在那里。

yingyinNormal.en: They got walls, fences, plots of land for farming. We could live there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们有围墙栅栏，可供耕种的土地，我们可以住在那里。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, I did in fact survive on a deserted planet by farming in my own shit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我确实在一个荒芜的星球上活下来了，靠着用自己的屎种地。

yingyinNormal.en: Ln South Korea, in the Wando Archipelago, over 200 islands have converted to farming seaweeds.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在韩国的莞岛群岛，超过200座岛屿已经用来种植海藻。

yingyinNormal.en: I am. But I'm allowed to be nervous. Intensive farming's a big step. Half past eight. I must skedaddle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是答应了，但有点紧张总可以吧，密集农作可是一大步。八点半了，我得走了。

yingyinNormal.en: Clearly, I made a good choice farming this out to you. But I am telling you, Amy hit the boyfriend jackpot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很明显，把此事交给你来办真是太英明了，你得知道，艾米找到我做男朋友可真是中了头奖。

yingyinNormal.en: My spies tell me that in order to starve the rebels out, we must cut them off from the farming village of Wuchang.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的探子告诉我为了饿死那些残党，我们必须断了他们和武昌之间的粮道。

yingyinNormal.en: But here some have turned to farming a crop that doesn't grow on land but well below the waves: the seaweed called giant kelp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是在这儿，有人转为种植庄稼。这种庄稼并非生长于大地上，而是繁盛在水波之下。这些水藻被称作巨型海带。

yingyinNormal.en: I began as a common man, farming in my fields in Nanyang, doing what I could to survive in an age of chaos. I never had any interest in making a name for myself as a noble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 臣本布衣，躬耕于南阳，苟全性命于乱世，不求闻达于诸侯。
